Coke studio is all about music which represents the soil of our nation... Computerized music is good but  according to me it was too much in this song!! 
I have watched too many coke studio Pakistan songs or Indian coke studio too , the best part was the synchronisation and entwined twinning of musicians with vocals... 
Somehow that element seemed missing!! For me, it was 5/10
Hope coke studio bharat will read this ..
